ELECTONICS
Electricity-a form of energy resulting from the existence of charged particles
current-flow of electrons in a conductor
voltage-PD
Sources of Electricity-solar,mains electricity,drycells,wind,geothermal,nuclear
isolaters help to separate areas that require power from those that don't
semi-conductors--conduct electricity at certain conditions(like doping...which is introducing foreign material in semiconductor eg phosphorus)




